# Alias ( Donâ€™t use it with OhMyBash)

```bash
mkdir -p ~/.bash_aliases 
```

add to `~/.bashrc`
```bash
if [ -f ~/.bash_aliases ]; then
.  ~/.bash_aliases
fi
```

```bash
source ~/.bashrc && source ~/.bash_aliases
```

add to `~/.bashrc`
```bash
alias pbcopy='xclip -selection clipboard'
alias ll='ls -a'
```
# Install OhMyBash
[Oh My Bash Repository - Docs ](https://github.com/ohmybash/oh-my-bash#via-curl)

- Install via `wget`
```bash
bash -c "$(wget https://raw.githubusercontent.com/ohmybash/oh-my-bash/master/tools/install.sh -O -)"
```

- update `~/.bash_profile`

```bash
if [[ -f ~/.bashrc ]]; then
  source ~/.bashrc
fi
```

